            "question": "What validation error would occur in this HTML5 form with constraint validation?\n[CODE]<form>\n  <div>\n    <label for=\"email\">Email Address</label>\n    <input type=\"email\" id=\"email\" name=\"email\" required>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label for=\"age\">Age</label>\n    <input type=\"number\" id=\"age\" name=\"age\" min=\"18\" max=\"120\" step=\"1\">\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label for=\"website\">Personal Website</label>\n    <input type=\"url\" id=\"website\" name=\"website\" pattern=\"https?://.+\">\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label for=\"password\">Password</label>\n    <input type=\"password\" id=\"password\" name=\"password\" \n           minlength=\"8\" maxlength=\"100\"\n           pattern=\"^(?=.*[a-z])(?=.*[A-Z])(?=.*\\d).{8,}$\">\n  </div>\n  \n  <div>\n    <label for=\"birthdate\">Birth Date</label>\n    <input type=\"date\" id=\"birthdate\" name=\"birthdate\" \n           min=\"1900-01-01\" max=\"2024-12-31\">\n  </div>\n  \n  <button type=\"submit\">Register</button>\n</form>[/CODE]",
